Add website products to your site, with layout and styling customizations. 


== Description ==
Add website products to your site, with layout and styling customizations.  Use the shortcode [website_products] where you want to output products.  
There is also a second shortcode, [website_products_index], for when when you wish to create products on another page such as the index.  
This different layout includes links to your products page, and in the plugin settings you can set a different header text too. 


== Frequently Asked Questions ==
=Can you set the number of products visible per row?=
Yes, you can.

=Is the header text customizable?=
Yes, the header text is customizable on both the "home" page and the "product" page.


== Installation == 
1. Upload the 'website-products' folder in '/wp-content/plugins' directory.
2. Activate the plugin in the Plugins menu in WordPress.


